                            <comment id="17216733" author="jira-bot" created="Mon, 19 Oct 2020 13:46:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit d5531e9b7f98a535bf952fabc4f5c07ffbfe6406 in lucene-solr&apos;s branch refs/heads/branch_8_7 from Kevin Risden&lt;br/&gt;
